# Maintainer playbook (local only)

Copy this file to **`MAINTAINER.md`** in the bundle root. `MAINTAINER.md` is gitignored — do not commit org names, internal repo slugs, or machine-specific paths.

## Local setup

| Field | Your value |
|-------|------------|
| `WORKFLOWS_BUNDLE_PATH` | e.g. `~/Repos/lsi/current/cursor-dev-workflows` |
| Internal source repo (if any) | `ORG/internal-cursor-dev-workflows` |
| Default adoption target(s) | App repo name(s), `CANONICAL_DOCS_PATH`, `ADOPTION_PROFILE` (A or B) |
| Default profile | **A — mirror bundle** (see [docs/adoption-layout.md](docs/adoption-layout.md)) |

## Sync mapping

Bundle path → adopted path in application repo(s). Default is **Profile A** ([docs/adoption-layout.md](docs/adoption-layout.md)):

| Bundle | Adopted in `<APP_REPO>` (Profile A) |
|--------|-------------------------------------|
| `docs/workflows/*.md` | `docs/workflows/*.md` (or your `CANONICAL_DOCS_PATH`) |
| `which-workflow.md` | **app repo root** |
| `templates/`, `examples/` | **app repo root** |
| `snippets/cursor-rules/*.mdc` | `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` |
| `AGENTS.md` | `AGENTS.md` (merge or replace per team) |

Profile **B** (flatten): router, templates, and examples under `CANONICAL_DOCS_PATH` with mandatory link rewrites — document in this table if a target uses B.

Add rows for any team-specific overrides.

## Pre-release checklist

Before bumping [VERSION](VERSION) or tagging:

- [ ] Diff `docs/workflows/`, `snippets/cursor-rules/`, `templates/`, `examples/` against last release
- [ ] Classify changes per [docs/versioning.md](docs/versioning.md) (MAJOR / MINOR / PATCH)
- [ ] Update `## [Unreleased]` in [CHANGELOG.md](CHANGELOG.md) with **Adopter action** bullets for MAJOR changes
- [ ] Run [adoption-checklist.md](adoption-checklist.md) §9 link verification + agent smoke on a sample app repo (Profile A)

## Release checklist

- [ ] Move `[Unreleased]` entries to `## [X.Y.Z] - YYYY-MM-DD` in [CHANGELOG.md](CHANGELOG.md)
- [ ] Set [VERSION](VERSION) to `X.Y.Z`
- [ ] Commit on `main` (e.g. `chore(release): mark bundle vX.Y.Z`)
- [ ] Tag: `git tag -a vX.Y.Z -m "cursor-dev-workflows vX.Y.Z"`
- [ ] Push tag when ready: `git push origin vX.Y.Z`
- [ ] Optional: GitHub Release — paste the `X.Y.Z` section from the changelog

## Adopter comms (MAJOR releases)

When shipping a **MAJOR** bump, tell adopters to:

1. Re-sync `CANONICAL_DOCS_PATH` from `docs/workflows/`
2. Re-copy and path-fix `snippets/cursor-rules/*.mdc`
3. Update `BUNDLE_VERSION` in their `PROJECT.md`
4. Read **Adopter action** in [CHANGELOG.md](CHANGELOG.md) for that version

## Sync from upstream (ongoing)

When merging bundle updates into an adopted app repo:

1. Diff each workflow file under `CANONICAL_DOCS_PATH` (and root `which-workflow.md`, `templates/`, `examples/` if Profile A)
2. Re-run link verification per [docs/adoption-layout.md](docs/adoption-layout.md) before merge
3. Record sync date and `BUNDLE_VERSION` (tag or SHA) in the app repo commit message or `PROJECT.md`
4. Do not commit this file or absolute clone paths into the app repo
